L4D2 coop save weapon when map transition if more than 4 players

-Changelog-
v5.2
-Remake code
-Add ConVar and generate cfg
-Support every round start if survivors wipe out

v4.1
-Original Post: https://forums.alliedmods.net/showthread.php?t=263860

-ConVar-
cfg/sourcemod/l4d2_ty_saveweapon.cfg
// Do not restore weapons and items to new player after survivors have left start safe area for at least x seconds. (0=Always restore)
l4d2_ty_saveweapon_game_seconds_block "100"

// If 1, restore full health when end of chapter.
l4d2_ty_saveweapon_health "0"

-Command-
None